      "description": "Our Hero, such as he is. Dexter Douglas was a computer nerd, in the early days of the Internet when that really meant something, until one fateful Christmas when his parents bought him a Pinnacle computer chip, the newest and most powerful on the market. Unbeknownst to Dexter, the chip contained a very particular flaw; if the user entered a specific computer key sequence while connected to the Internet, the chip would overload, and forcibly merge the user's mind with all the information of the online world. You can probably guess what happened next. Alliterative Name:DexterDouglas. Butt-Monkey: He has aBig Brother Bully, no friends, and girls repeatedly turn him down for dates. Cursed with Awesome: He wasn't too happy at first about becoming Freakazoid, but once he realized theopportunities(code: impressing girls) his attitude changed. Demoted to Extra: After appearing on a semi-regular basis in season 1, season 2 sees Dexter make only two appearance in the premiere episode, Dexter’s Date and the third episode, Mission: Freakazoid. Afterwards, the only thing to remind audiences that Dexter exists is his appearance in the theme song.",
