      "description": "The creator of the Pinnacle computer chip, and the first person to realize the flaw it contained, Roddy sought out Dexter that fateful Christmas and helped train him to use his new powers. Badass Normal: He has no powers, but is a helpful ally to Freakazoid. Even after exposing himself to the same flaw that created Freakazoid, the only power he gains is the ability to travel through the Internet. Brave Scot: Often participates in Freakazoids missions, despite not having the same powers aside from the ability to move through the Internet. Cassandra Truth: Was the one to discover the flaw in the Pinnacle computer chip, and calculated the effect it would have. When he went to the board of directors with his findings, Armando Guitierrez threw him out a window to keep him silent and prevent a recall. Eccentric Mentor: To Freakazoid.",
