      "description": "AMad Scientistand Freakazoid'sArch-Enemy, to the extent the concept even applies to the teen hero, The Lobe is a hideously mutated supervillain whose brain has consumed his entire head and seeks nothing short of world domination... well, except on Christmas. Affably Evil: He's out to control the world and destroy his hated enemy, but that doesn't mean he's not polite and pleasant. Arch-Enemy: To Freakazoid. Big Bad: He's the most frequently seen villain. He also serves as the leader of the rogues gallery (such as it is) whenever they team up. Deadpan Snarker: Freakazoid's antics usually bring out his sarcastic side.",
